extend layout
block content
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/popmotion.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/index.css')
    .content
        #builder
        h1 LTDStats.com - Statistics, Guides, Player Profiles and more!
        p.
        .tabmenu
            .tab_top_active#tab_top_1(onclick="javascript:openTab(1);") News
            .tab_top_passive#tab_top_2(onclick="javascript:openTab(2);") Content
            .style(style='clear: both;')
            .tab_box#tab_box_1
                .newsbox
                    .news
                        | Atlantean Legion released with patch v2.34!
                        br
                        | Check out the 
                        a(href="/ladder/atlantean") Atlantean Ladder
                        |  to look up top Atlantean players and their builds.
                        p
                        i 2018-08-08 GvR Mr Mister
                    .news
                        | Legion TD 2 Masters Cup II:
                        br
                        | Date: 11/12th of August 2018
                        br
                        | Check out the best Legion TD 2 Teams fighting for >$400 in the
                        a(href="/tournaments")  Masters Cup II.
                        p
                        i 2018-07-31 GvR Mr Mister
                    .news
                        | Added statistics:
                        br
                        | Player Elo Distribution, Legion Pick/Winrates, Workers per Wave, Networth per Wave, Value on game end, Workers on game end, Income on game end and Leaks on game end.
                        p
                        i 2018-07-24 GvR Mr Mister
                    .news
                        | Want to contribute?
                        br
                        | For all of you that have experience in webdesign/coding may look into this: 
                        a(href="https://github.com/Shoro2/ltdstats", target="blank") LTDStats GitHub Project
                        p
                        i 2018-07-24 GvR Mr Mister
                    .news
                        | Next-to-add:
                        br
                        | More statistics, detailed help section (/help), guides layout, compare layout, livegame lookup
                        p
                        i 2018-07-24 GvR Mr Mister
            .tab_box#tab_box_2
                    .contentbox
                        b Profile
                        p Check out statistics, elograph, the matchhistory, collection and players ingame behaviour. 
                            a(href="/help/profile")
                                img(src="/img/icons/qmark.png", title="Help", width="15px", height="15px", style="margin:5px; float:right;")
                        p
                            img.indexbild(src="/img/profile.png")
                        b Ladder
                        p Check out your rank or top 100 in the offical ladder.
                            a(href="/help/ladder")
                                img(src="/img/icons/qmark.png", title="Help", width="15px", height="15px", style="margin:5px; float:right;")
                        p
                            img.indexbild(src="/img/ladder.png")
                        b Replay
                        p Look up your game for detailed information about it.
                            a(href="/help/replay")
                                    img(src="/img/icons/qmark.png", title="Help", width="15px", height="15px", style="margin:5px; float:right;")
                        p
                            img.indexbild(src="/img/replay.png")
                        b Compare
                        p Compare two players.
                            a(href="/help/compare")
                                img(src="/img/icons/qmark.png", title="Help", width="15px", height="15px", style="margin:5px; float:right;")
                        p
                            img.indexbild(src="/img/compare.png")
                        b Builder
                        p Share your perfect build with <a href="https://github.com/attrib/legion2-builder">Attrib's Builder Tool</a>.
                            a(href="/help/builder")
                                img(src="/img/icons/qmark.png", title="Help", width="15px", height="15px", style="margin:5px; float:right;")
                        p
                            img.indexbild(src="/img/builder.png" width="1100px")
                        b Units
                        p Look up any fighter, mercanery or wave unit.
                            a(href="/help/units")
                                img(src="/img/icons/qmark.png", title="Help", width="15px", height="15px", style="margin:5px; float:right;")
                        p
                            img.indexbild(src="/img/units.png" width="1100px")
                        b Guides
                        p Here you can find guides for all races and general hints.
                            a(href="/help/guides")
                                img(src="/img/icons/qmark.png", title="Help", width="15px", height="15px", style="margin:5px; float:right;")
                        p
                            img.indexbild(src="/img/guides.png" width="1100px")
                        b Statistics
                        p Provides you detailled statistic about specific patches/days/players or overall data.
                            a(href="/help/statistics")
                                img(src="/img/icons/qmark.png", title="Help", width="15px", height="15px", style="margin:5px; float:right;")
                        p
                            img.indexbild(src="/img/statistics.png" width="1100px")
    script(src="/js/jquery.js")                    
    script(src="/js/tabmenu.js")
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/tabmenu.css')
    script openTab(1);
